comments: Jokic (DEN) engages and disengages with Davis (LAL) off-ball.
Davis (LAL) rests his hands on Grant's (LAL) backside as he sets the pick and quickly releases as he begins to roll to the basket.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Caruso's (LAL) path and gives Caruso room to avoid the contact.
Millsap (DEN) makes marginal contact to James' (LAL) backside while rebounding.
Grant (DEN) maintains legal guarding position as James (LAL) loses his balance on his own at the end of the drive.
James (LAL) loses his balance and makes incidental contact with Millsap's (DEN) lower half after losing control of the ball in the lane.
Caruso (LAL) is turning slightly as he goes over the pick and marginal body contact occurs with Murray (DEN).
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Caruso's (LAL) path and absorbs the side-to-side contact.
James (LAL) and Grant (DEN) engage and disengage with one one another during the inbound.
Millsap (DEN) and Caldwell-Pope (LAL) engage and disengage with one another as they move over the screen.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) and Murray (DEN) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Dozier (DEN) does not bring any part of his hand underneath the ball and he legally continues his dribble after briefly losing control.
Caldwell-Pope (LAL) has his right arm slightly extended outward as contact occurs with Murray's (DEN) left arm/side at the top of the perimeter, but it is marginal.

Caldwell-Pope (LAL) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Murray (DEN) after the release of his jump shot attempt. Caldwell-Pope jumps  to defend Murray's jump shot attempt and would land ahead of Murray; Murray extends his leg into Caldwell-Pope.
Jokic (DEN) and James (LAL) engage and disengage with one another as they each attempt to gain rebounding position.

James (LAL) makes marginal contact with Jokic's (DEN) right wrist as Jokic gains control of the rebound and simultaneously attempts the shot. Jokic releases the shot attempt prior to the expiration of the shot clock.
Jokic's (DEN) left hand is extended slightly forward as contact occurs with Davis (LAL) during the driving shot attempt, but it is marginal and Davis absorbs it.
Dozier (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position and moves parallel alongside Davis' (DEN) path on his driving shot attempt.
Dozier (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Davis' (LAL) path and does not deliver the contact.
Davis (LAL) makes marginal contact to Jokic's (DEN) front at the start of his drive.
Davis (LAL) maintains verticality and legally contests Jokic's (DEN) shot attempt in the lane.
Grant (DEN) brushes James' (LAL) backside as James stops his forward momentum in the lane during the inbound.
Green (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Grant's (DEN) path and does not deliver the contact.
Murray (DEN) maintains legal guarding position as body contact occurs with James (LAL) at the end of the drive.
Jokic (DEN) is in the lane when the clock starts and he then separates from Davis (LAL).  He is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds and then fully exits.
James (LAL) engages and disengages with Murray (DEN) after the release of the jump shot attempt.
James (LAL) and Millsap (DEN) make incidental arm contact with one another during rebounding.
Green (LAL) makes incidental contact with Murray's (DEN) arm after cleanly poking the ball free during rebounding.
Murray (DEN) cleanly blocks Green's (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) legally contests Davis' (LAL) jump shot attempt.
